### Hotel Hub API - Hotel Management Endpoints
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080

### Get all hotels (basic)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/hotels

###

### Get all hotels with pagination
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/hotels?page=0&size=10

###

### Get hotels with city filter
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/hotels?city=Paris

###

### Get hotels with country filter  
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/hotels?country=FR

###

### Get hotels with star rating filter
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/hotels?minStars=3&maxStars=5

###

### Get hotels with rating filter
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/hotels?minRating=7.0&maxRating=9.5

###

### Get hotels with multiple filters
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/hotels?city=Paris&country=FR&minStars=4&minRating=8.0&page=0&size=5

###

### Search hotels by query
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/hotels/search?q=luxury

###

### Search hotels by location
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/hotels/search?q=London

###

### Search hotels with pagination
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/hotels/search?q=hotel&page=0&size=5

###

### Get hotel statistics
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/hotels/stats

###